Resource Profile: openIMIS Communication

Official URL: https://github.com/openimis/openimis_fhir_r5_ig/StructureDefinition/openimis-communication Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2025-08-26 Computable Name: OpenIMISCommunication

Defines a Communication for openIMIS which maps to the Feedback in openIMIS.

Usages:

  • Examples for this Profile: Communication/Claim001Communication
  • CapabilityStatements using this Profile: openIMIS Capability Statement

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
